                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-8 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-郭水龍/Keh Chuí-lêng]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13187.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13187.htm">諒解 [ Liōng-kái ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">諒解
        芥菜子第 6號「喜出望外」欄內羅居的目睭內障的病。蘭醫生佮馬偕醫院無共伊手術是因為猶未熟，請列位著諒解。...<a href="artical-13187.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/49f530da2e789.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/49f530da2e789.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
